20: The menu bar icon changes colour based on your usage levels:
40: </p>
80: Chrome, Arc, Brave, Edge, and other Chromium browsers may ask for browser Safe Storage Keychain access so Pinemeter can decrypt cookies. Safari cookies are protected by macOS and may require Full Disk Access.
